14#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_AVC_258_C
15#define RDATA_GENERIC_AVC_258_C
16
17#define RRTYPE_AVC_ATTRIBUTES (0)
18
19static inline isc_result_t
20fromtext_avc(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
21
22 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_avc);
23
24 UNUSED(type);
25 UNUSED(rdclass);
26 UNUSED(origin);
27 UNUSED(options);
28 UNUSED(callbacks);
29
30 return (generic_fromtext_txt(rdclass, type, lexer, origin, options,
31 target, callbacks));
32}
33
34static inline isc_result_t
35totext_avc(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
36
37 UNUSED(tctx);
38
39 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_avc);
40
41 return (generic_totext_txt(rdata, tctx, target));
42}
43
44static inline isc_result_t
45fromwire_avc(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
46
47 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_avc);
48
49 UNUSED(type);
50 UNUSED(dctx);
51 UNUSED(rdclass);
52 UNUSED(options);
53
54 return (generic_fromwire_txt(rdclass, type, source, dctx, options,
55 target));
56}
57
58static inline isc_result_t
59towire_avc(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
60
61 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_avc);
62
63 UNUSED(cctx);
64
65 return (mem_tobuffer(target, rdata->data, rdata->length));
66}
67
68static inline int
69compare_avc(ARGS_COMPARE) {
70 isc_region_t r1;
71 isc_region_t r2;
72
73 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
74 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
75 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_avc);
76
77 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
78 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
79 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
80}
81
82static inline isc_result_t
83fromstruct_avc(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
84
85 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_avc);
86
87 return (generic_fromstruct_txt(rdclass, type, source, target));
88}
89
90static inline isc_result_t
91tostruct_avc(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
92 dns_rdata_avc_t *avc = target;
93
94 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_avc);
95 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
96
97 avc->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
98 avc->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
99 ISC_LINK_INIT(&avc->common, link);
100
101 return (generic_tostruct_txt(rdata, target, mctx));
102}
103
104static inline void
105freestruct_avc(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
106 dns_rdata_avc_t *txt = source;
107
108 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
109 REQUIRE(txt->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_avc);
110
111 generic_freestruct_txt(source);
112}
113
114static inline isc_result_t
115additionaldata_avc(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
116 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_avc);
117
118 UNUSED(rdata);
119 UNUSED(add);
120 UNUSED(arg);
121
122 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
123}
124
125static inline isc_result_t
126digest_avc(ARGS_DIGEST) {
127 isc_region_t r;
128
129 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_avc);
130
131 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
132
133 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
134}
135
136static inline bool
137checkowner_avc(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
138
139 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_avc);
140
141 UNUSED(name);
142 UNUSED(type);
143 UNUSED(rdclass);
144 UNUSED(wildcard);
145
146 return (true);
147}
148
149static inline bool
150checknames_avc(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
151
152 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_avc);
153
154 UNUSED(rdata);
155 UNUSED(owner);
156 UNUSED(bad);
157
158 return (true);
159}
160
161static inline int
162casecompare_avc(ARGS_COMPARE) {
163 return (compare_avc(rdata1, rdata2));
164}
165#endif /* RDATA_GENERIC_AVC_258_C */
